if you don't want to be expelled,

165
00:07:33,390 --> 00:07:34,630
you must strictly follow

166
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:36,560
Jingcai College's rules and regulations.

167
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,620
Do you understand?

168
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,980
Yes, I understand.

169
