286
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:06,390
Got it,

287
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:08,270
Mom.

288
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:27,850
Jiang Bohan.

289
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,510
