293
00:14:45,750 --> 00:14:47,950
It has nothing to do with that incident.

294
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:49,630
Moreover,

295
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,530
you've crossed a line.

296
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:55,200
I crossed a line?

297
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:58,240
So you’re treating me like this

298
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:00,560
all because of that Yu Mingxi?

299
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:06,010
You asked me to stay away from you.

300
00:15:06,110 --> 00:15:06,750
I agreed.

301
00:15:08,270 --> 00:15:09,840
I joined the cheerleading squad to watch you from afar

302
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:10,770
and cheer you on.

303
00:15:11,590 --> 00:15:12,650
But what about you?

304
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:14,440
I didn't give you space

305
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:14,840
so you could

306
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:16,360
date someone else.

307
00:15:20,610 --> 00:15:21,660
Give me space?

308
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,240
Where do you get the confidence

309
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,390
to say such things?

310
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,080
Confidence?

311
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,600
We've been childhood sweethearts

312
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,800
and grew up together.

313
00:15:30,980 --> 00:15:35,240
If anyone has the right to speak with confidence, it's me, Qin Siyao, not her!

314
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,030
In terms of family background,

315
00:15:36,030 --> 00:15:36,720
grades,

316
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:37,240
and looks,

317
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,720
how am I inferior to her in any way?

318
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:41,080
I have never judged someone's worth

319
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:42,460
based on material things,

320
00:15:42,460 --> 00:15:43,670
Moreover, you're too obsessive.

321
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:44,270
The things you did...

322
00:15:44,270 --> 00:15:45,000
The things I did,

323
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:46,720
don't you know why I did them?

324
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,030
So I'm sorry

325
00:16:01,990 --> 00:16:02,920
that you like me.

326
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,880
All you have for me is an apology?

327
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:11,010
Then what do you feel for Yu Mingxi?

328
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,890
None of your business.

329
00:16:16,630 --> 00:16:17,440
Jiang Bohan!

330
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:18,910
If you dare to like her,

331
00:16:18,910 --> 00:16:20,390
I'll never let her off!

332
00:16:43,430 --> 00:16:44,630
Go ahead and try then.

333
00:16:50,730 --> 00:16:54,960
[Close to You]
